QuestData.Title: Archivum Data Disc
QuestData.Description: This platinum disc is surprisingly symmetrical and devoid of any scratches or imperfections. Engraved along its edge, bold runes spell out the word "ARCHIVUM."$B$BThere must be a device inside Ulduar capable of reading the disc.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Archivum Data Disc to the Archivum Console in Ulduar.
QuestData.CompletionText: The console whirrs with energy as the round receptacle opens.
QuestData.RewardText: The platinum disc fits perfectly inside the console. It begins to spin as its contents are scanned by white beams of light.
